                    <comment id="12576880" author="doronc" created="Mon, 10 Mar 2008 06:57:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Trejkaz thanks for the patch. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached a slightly compacted fix (refactoring slop-applying to a separate method).&lt;br/&gt;
Also added a test that fails without this fix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All tests pass, if there are no comments I will commit this in a day or two.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
